SQL_STMT_U.val: select h.DocEntry, h.ObjType, h.Status, h.Canceled, h.FinncPriod, h.DocDate, h.DocNum, h.CardName, p.PrcName, h.DocType, iif(trim(h.DocType) = 'A', 'Account', iif(trim(h.DocType) = 'C', 'Customer', 'Supplier')) as DocTypeFullDesc, h.CounterRef, replace(replace(replace(h.Comments,char(13),' '),char(10),''),char(9),'') as Comments, h.DocCurr, h.CashSum, h.TrsfrSum, h.CheckSum, r3.CreditSum, r4.SumApplied, h.BcgSum, h.DocTotal, iif(trim(h.Status)='O', 'Open', iif(trim(h.Status)='D', 'Draft', 'Closed')) as [StatusFullDesc], h.TrackNo, concat( iif(isnull(h.CashAcct,'')='', '', h.CashAcct), '/', iif(isnull(h.TrsfrAcct,'')='', '', h.TrsfrAcct), '/', iif(isnull(h.CheckAcct,'')='', '', h.CheckAcct), '/', iif(isnull(r3.CreditAcct,'')='', '', r3.CreditAcct), '/', iif(isnull(r4.AcctCode,'')='', '', r4.AcctCode) ) as PaymentAcctCode, concat( iif(isnull(a1.AcctName,'')='', '', a1.AcctName), '/', iif(isnull(a2.AcctName,'')='', '', a2.AcctName), '/', iif(isnull(a3.AcctName,'')='', '', a3.AcctName), '/', iif(isnull(r3.CreditName,'')='', '', r3.CreditName), '/', iif(isnull(r4.AcctName,'')='', '', r4.AcctName) ) as PaymentAcctName from orct h left join oprc p on h.U_IDU_Kode_PT = p.PrcCode left join ( select r3i.docnum, STRING_AGG(r3i.CreditAcct, ',') as CreditAcct, STRING_AGG(a3i.AcctName, ',') as CreditName, SUM(r3i.CreditSum) as CreditSum from rct3 r3i left join oact a3i on r3i.CreditAcct = a3i.AcctCode group by r3i.DocNum ) r3 on h.DocEntry = r3.DocNum left join ( select r4i.docnum, STRING_AGG(r4i.AcctCode, ',') as AcctCode, STRING_AGG(r4i.AcctName, ',') as AcctName, SUM(r4i.SumApplied) as SumApplied from rct4 r4i group by r4i.DocNum ) r4 on h.DocEntry = r4.DocNum left join oact a1 on a1.acctcode = h.CashAcct left join oact a2 on a2.acctcode = h.TrsfrAcct left join oact a3 on a3.acctcode = h.CheckAcct where (ISNULL(h.CardName,'') like '%'+ISNULL(':2','')+'%') and (h.DocDate between ':3' and ':4') and h.DocType like ':5' and h.DocNum like '%'+ISNULL(':1','')+'%' and h.canceled <> 'C' and (h.Canceled = ':6' or ':6' is null or ':6' = '') and (upper(isnull(h.CounterRef,'')) like '%'+ISNULL(':7','')+'%') :8 :9 :10 :11 :12 order by h.docentry desc

SQL_STMT_U.val: select sum(total) as TotalData, STRING_AGG(FromToData, '/') as [FromToData] from ( select top 10000 count(1) as total, concat(min(DocEntry), '|', max(DocEntry)) as FromToData from ( select (ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY h.DOCENTRY DESC) / :13) AS GroupData, h.DocEntry from orct h (nolock) left join oprc p (nolock) on h.U_IDU_Kode_PT = p.PrcCode left join ( select r3i.docnum, STRING_AGG(r3i.CreditAcct, ',') as CreditAcct, STRING_AGG(a3i.AcctName, ',') as CreditName, SUM(r3i.CreditSum) as CreditSum from rct3 r3i (nolock) left join oact a3i (nolock) on r3i.CreditAcct = a3i.AcctCode group by r3i.DocNum ) r3 on h.DocEntry = r3.DocNum left join ( select r4i.docnum, STRING_AGG(r4i.AcctCode, ',') as AcctCode, STRING_AGG(r4i.AcctName, ',') as AcctName, SUM(r4i.SumApplied) as SumApplied from rct4 r4i (nolock) group by r4i.DocNum ) r4 on h.DocEntry = r4.DocNum left join oact a1 (nolock) on a1.acctcode = h.CashAcct left join oact a2 (nolock) on a2.acctcode = h.TrsfrAcct left join oact a3 (nolock) on a3.acctcode = h.CheckAcct where (h.DocDate between ':3' and ':4') and h.canceled <> 'C' :2 :5 :1 :6 :7 :8 :9 :10 :11 :12 :14 ) T group by T.GroupData order by T.GroupData ) A
